gdom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1973}}\n| 7 April\n| {{Esc|Luxembourg}}\n| \"[[Tu te reconna\u00eetras]]\"\n| [[Anne-Marie David]]\n| French\n| {{nts|129}}\n| {{nts|4}}\n| {{Esc|Spain|1945}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1974}}\n| 6 April\n| {{Esc|Sweden}}\n| \"[[Waterloo (ABBA song)|Waterloo]]\"\n| [[ABBA]]\n| English\n| {{nts|24}}\n| {{nts|6}}\n| {{Esc|Italy}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1975}}\n| 22 March\n| {{Esc|Netherlands}}\n| \"[[Ding-a-dong]]\"\n| [[Teach-In (band)|Teach-In]]\n| English\n| {{nts|152}}\n| {{nts|14}}\n| {{Esc|United Kingdom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1976}}\n| 3 April\n| {{Esc|United Kingdom}}\n| \"[[Save Your Kisses for Me]]\"\n| [[Brotherhood of Man]]\n| English\n| {{nts|164}}\n| {{nts|17}}\n| {{Esc|France}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1977}}\n| 7 May\n| {{Esc|France}}\n| \"[[L'oiseau et l'enfant]]\"\n| [[Marie Myriam]]\n| French\n| {{nts|136}}\n| {{nts|15}}\n| {{Esc|United Kingdom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1978}}\n| 22 April\n| {{Esc|Israel}}\n| \"[[A-Ba-Ni-Bi]]\" <small>({{transl|he|\u05d0-\u05d1-\u05e0\u05d9-\u05d1\u05d9}})</small>\n| [[Izhar Cohen]] and the [[Alphabeta]]\n| [[Hebrew]]\n| {{nts|157}}\n| {{nts|32}}\n| {{Esc|Belgium}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1979}}\n| 31 March\n| {{Esc|Israel}}\n| \"[[Hallelujah (Milk and Honey song)|Hallelujah]]\" <small>({{transl|he|\u05d4\u05dc\u05dc\u05d5\u05d9\u05d4}})</small>\n| [[Milk and Honey (group)|Milk and Honey]]\n| Hebrew\n| {{nts|125}}\n| {{nts|9}}\n| {{Esc|Spain|1977}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1980}}\n| 19 April\n| {{Esc|Ireland}}\n| \"[[What's Another Year]]\"\n| [[Johnny Logan (singer)|Johnny Logan]]\n| English\n| {{nts|143}}\n| {{nts|15}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" | {{Esc|Germany}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1981}}\n| 4 April\n| {{Es