\n| {{Esc|Luxembourg}}\n| \"[[Poup\u00e9e de cire, poup\u00e9e de son]]\"\n| [[France Gall]]\n| French\n| {{nts|32}}\n| {{nts|6}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1966}}\n| 5 March\n| {{Esc|Austria}}\n| \"[[Merci, Ch\u00e9rie]]\"\n| [[Udo J\u00fcrgens]]\n| [[German language|German]]\n| {{nts|31}}\n| {{nts|15}}\n| {{Esc|Sweden}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1967}}\n| 8 April\n| {{Esc|United Kingdom}}\n| \"[[Puppet on a String]]\"\n| [[Sandie Shaw]]\n| [[English language|English]]\n| {{nts|47}}\n| {{nts|25}}\n| {{Esc|Ireland}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1968}}\n| 6 April\n| {{Esc|Spain|1945}}\n| \"[[La, la, la]]\"\n| [[Massiel]]\n| [[Spanish language|Spanish]]\n| {{nts|29}}\n| {{nts|1}}\n| {{Esc|United Kingdom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"rowspan=4|{{escyr|1969}}\n|rowspan=4| 29 March\n| {{Esc|Spain|1945}}\n| \"[[Vivo cantando]]\"\n| [[Salom\u00e9 (singer)|Salom\u00e9]]\n| Spanish\n|rowspan=4|{{nts|18}}\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"4\" {{N/A|''No runner-up''}}\n|-\n| {{Esc|United Kingdom}}\n| \"[[Boom Bang-a-Bang]]\"\n| [[Lulu (singer)|Lulu]]\n| English\n|-\n| {{Esc|Netherlands}}\n| \"[[De troubadour]]\"\n| [[Lenny Kuhr]]\n| Dutch\n|-\n| {{Esc|France}}\n| \"[[Un jour, un enfant]]\"\n| [[Frida Boccara]]\n| French\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1970}}\n| 21 March\n| {{Esc|Ireland}}\n| \"[[All Kinds of Everything]]\"\n| [[Dana Rosemary Scallon|Dana]]\n| English\n| {{nts|32}}\n| {{nts|6}}\n| {{Esc|United Kingdom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1971}}\n| 3 April\n| {{Esc|Monaco}}\n| \"[[Un banc, un arbre, une rue]]\"\n| [[S\u00e9verine (singer)|S\u00e9verine]]\n| French\n| {{nts|128}}\n| {{nts|12}}\n| {{Esc|Spain|1945}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left\"| {{escyr|1972}}\n| 25 March\n| {{Esc|Luxembourg}}\n| \"[[Apr\u00e8s toi]]\"\n| [[Vicky Leandros]]\n| French\n| {{nts|128}}\n| {{nts|14}}\n| {{Esc|United Kingdom}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\